trino-monaco
============

This project includes code adapted from third-party open-source software.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Monaco Editor (microsoft/monaco-editor)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Trino Monarch tokenizer and language configuration in
`src/trino/language.ts` are adapted from the Monaco Editor SQL language
definition (`src/basic-languages/sql/sql.ts`), with modifications for the
Trino SQL grammar.

